Let’s be honest…
Those wives at the party, laughing, glowing, unbothered?
They’re not just lucky.
They’re loved. Relaxed. Chosen.
Because a man who plans the night, books the table, and shows up—
That man has a woman who doesn’t need to beg for attention.

We’re tired of doing it all.
Planning. Reminding. Begging for quality time.
We don’t want to carry the relationship or the calendar.

Sometimes the bare minimum isn’t flowers.
It’s presence. It’s effort.
It’s a man who understands the assignment. 💋🖤🥂
